<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV56">
<l>ilaṅkaimaṉṉa ṉaintoṭaintu paintalaini lattukak</l>
<l>kalaṅkavaṉṟu ceṉṟukoṉṟu veṉṟikoṇṭa vīraṉē</l>
<l>vilaṅkunūlar vētanāvar nītiyāṉa kēḷviyār</l>
<l>valaṅkoḷakku ṭantaiyuṭki ṭantamālu mallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Warrior who gained victory by going [to Laṅkā] on that day so that [Rāvaṇa] was</l>
<l rend="indent">Afraid, and killed [him]</l>
<l>in such a way that the ten strong heads of the king of Laṅkā dropped on the ground!</l>
<l>Aren’t you the Māl who reclined in Kuṭantai so that [Brahmins] with threads</l>
<l rend="indent">across [their chests],</l>
<l>—those with the Vedas on the [tip of their] tongues, those who had learned</l>
<l rend="indent">The right [knowledge]—circumambulate [You]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
